{
  "page": "Shield of Lannisport",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Shield of Lannisport</b> is a title bestowed upon the defender of the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>. Traditionally, the title is usually held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Lord of Casterly Rock\">Lord of Casterly Rock</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Shields_of_Lannisport\">Known Shields of Lannisport</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shield_of_Lannisport&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Shields of Lannisport\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Loren_Lannister\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Loren Lannister\">Loren Lannister</a>, <i>Loren the Last</i></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyman_Lannister\" title=\"Lyman Lannister\">Lyman Lannister</a></li>\n<li>Tymond's father<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tymond_Lannister\" title=\"Tymond Lannister\">Tymond Lannister</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Loreon_Lannister_(son_of_Jason)\" title=\"Loreon Lannister (son of Jason)\">Loreon Lannister</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Lannister_(lord)\" title=\"Damon Lannister (lord)\">Damon Lannister</a>, <i>the Grey Lion</i></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tybolt_Lannister\" title=\"Tybolt Lannister\">Tybolt Lannister</a></li>\n<li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Cerelle_Lannister_(daughter_of_Tybolt)\" title=\"Cerelle Lannister (daughter of Tybolt)\">Cerelle Lannister</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Lannister\" title=\"Gerold Lannister\">Gerold Lannister</a>, <i>Gerold the Golden</i></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Lannister\" title=\"Tytos Lannister\">Tytos Lannister</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a></li>\n<li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shield_of_Lannisport&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403122818\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 